    Hello,<br>
    For now, you have to look at PCI ids. NVIDIA GPUs have "10de:xxxx"
    as vendor/device ids, that's what is shown in your boxes on the
    right.<br>
    We should have better GPU support in the future. Right now, we only
    use what Linux knows, and it knows pretty much nothing about NVIDIA
    GPUs because of the closed-source driver :/<br>
    Brice<br>
    <br>
